Nutrient data for: VARIETY CAKE DONUTS, UPC: 011225127717

ENRICHED FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, VEGETABLE SHORTENING (PALM AND/OR COTTONSEED AND/OR CANOLA OIL), SUGAR, SOYBEAN OIL, DEFATTED SOY FLOUR, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: GLYCERIN, LEAVENING (SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, BAKING SODA, GLUCONO DELTA-LACTONE), DEXTROSE, WHEY PROTEIN CONCENTRATE, SALT, MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES, EGGS, SOY LECITHIN, GUAR GUM, SODIUM PROPIONATE AND POTASSIUM SORBATE (PRESERVATIVES), POLYSORBATE 60, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, ANNATTO AND TURMERIC EXTRACTS (COLOR), SPICE, XANTHAN GUM, CELLULOSE GUM, ENZYMES. IF POWDERED: MODIFIED CORN STARCH, PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN AND/OR COTTONSEED OILS, CALCIUM PROPIONATE (PRESERVATIVE). IF GLAZED W/CRUNCH: CORN SYRUP, CORN CEREAL, CORN STARCH, MALTODEXTRIN, CORN SYRUP SOLIDS, CALCIUM CARBONATE, CARAMEL COLOR, PAPRIKA EXTRACT, AGAR, BHT AND CITRIC ACID TO PROTECT FLAVOR, LOCUST BEAN GUM, CALCIUM SULFATE.
